snippet.title: EuroPython Conference
snippet.description:
The official YouTube Channel of the EuroPython conferences. Current edition: EuroPython 2021.

EuroPython is the official European conference for the Python programming language.

Copyright © 2004-2021, EuroPython Speakers, EuroPython Society, Sweden and the Local Organizers of the EuroPython conferences. "EuroPython" is a trademark of the EuroPython Society.

Photo references:
https://ep2021.europython.eu/imprint/
